rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Thank goodness we managed to
avoid all-out war! That would've
been a disaster, wouldn't it?

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0002
rows.name:
With nations at each other's throats,
trade would be awful, and nobody
would buy my woodcrafts!

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to share the wonders of
Gulan woodcraft with people
all across Alst!

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0004
rows.name:
War getting in the way of my dreams
would've been a real tragedy!
